metadata.name: Eclipse
metadata.description:
InitSound presents the first "Preset Pack From The Metaverse". 

50+ unique presets, Macro modulations, versatile sounds for Xfer Serum to use in your productions. 

PLEASE NOTE: This pack is ONLY available with this NFT. The auction winner will get an encrypted download link to get all the presets in one folder. 

No one will be able to find and use these sounds other than the NFT owner. This is the only way to make your productions unique and different from anyone else. 

Enjoy the revolution of sound design.
